      <title>When? v0.11.0</title>
      <link>https://play-when.com</link>
      <guid isPermaLink="false">when-v0.11.0</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Jun 2026 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
      <description><![CDATA[<h3>Features</h3><br/><br/><ul><li>Add advanced options (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/8cc2c134be3899823e2359f16611aa52b848baad">8cc2c13</a>)</li> <li>Add categories of events (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/72a57ef2c38106ece8bd79d663b363af3d57631b">72a57ef</a>)</li> <li>Add cloudinary image urls (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/0a8b205941de0828565db1f58dc2527e1e3f087a">0a8b205</a>)</li> <li>Add daily theme, clean up events (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/77ccaa5cb0ea4789ec6352ec73c69b326ad8abf2">77ccaa5</a>)</li> <li>Add description to incorrect card (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/3bc2cf0809de6a696383a3b60104a72e17399839">3bc2cf0</a>)</li> <li>Add extra share button and explaination (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/7141d489638f19b0b9903b8f61a0608285c202f7">7141d48</a>)</li> <li>Add feedback email button (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/cf03901f5bc86ccc34c6e131df6b17db6b2863b3">cf03901</a>)</li> <li>Add full timeline view (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/01d4d88cc868317058afc16b1f9a0dcdfd89e0a1">01d4d88</a>)</li> <li>Add game modes (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/8d66c6699192bbcb7d5bcfe1bf6faf8b3759685d">8d66c66</a>)</li> <li>Add game over screen (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/f4dad4c6b5cba352ad22eb373e6db58f04a85009">f4dad4c</a>)</li> <li>Add game stats (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/c472da978912ad3860cd6d0b46aa1f1968f863d6">c472da9</a>)</li> <li>Add global leaderboard (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/f3816dbd7cf41f103b87cd92c344ec849cdfad8a">f3816db</a>)</li> <li>Add hand mat (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/94b4d1e1173a8fd14267c1391f18015baa57c05a">94b4d1e</a>)</li> <li>Add hands, add hand cycling, fix awful z order bugs... (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/9d61b963a949c06150cd9535d62e520461823185">9d61b96</a>)</li> <li>Add haptic feedback (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/5f92efbe632ee91edbed594639bb58901444dbfd">5f92efb</a>)</li> <li>Add Haptics to card drag and drop (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/9b7a5c66f574930249855ac97527a7fab7669b5c">9b7a5c6</a>)</li> <li>Add images to new events (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/7c8f4b56c018b3cf6451f995ec2733d6cf027a1f">7c8f4b5</a>)</li> <li>Add info bar (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/1f761e6bcb5b4c809802b6562fa8b36654aeb466">1f761e6</a>)</li> <li>Add IOS haptics (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/8e49f7b650c60a60a13dcc6f2c4856d9c4db048e">8e49f7b</a>)</li> <li>Add leaderboard placeholder for loading (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/17ece49b06dd10992a25f3a7eaefeb6d4f54ef9c">17ece49</a>)</li> <li>Add many new events (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/c9f4bdf6be37be6ada145ddbcf8b9226876e6dc2">c9f4bdf</a>)</li> <li>Add many new events (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/8663d4c985c47342b1bad16c26bcdff57740ac80">8663d4c</a>)</li> <li>Add missing images (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/0367526da9025ad30532fe04bfd08d2867a1648e">0367526</a>)</li> <li>Add more events (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/5a5e632a8ac2964cea0bc17df42d04571029dc58">5a5e632</a>)</li> <li>Add more events (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/c08bd93b38f71f8658eca1f913f69200415f612c">c08bd93</a>)</li> <li>Add more events (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/31a44f7ed85bdb7bf629358d629bd96b6778ca3a">31a44f7</a>)</li> <li>Add more images (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/98e4fc1b2a00f7d202b7370cd56b5c92e8ec1252">98e4fc1</a>)</li> <li>Add more images (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/a824ca0654fc0258a9f31fdee284fa752659c88d">a824ca0</a>)</li> <li>Add more images (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/8000e00d70dbad49b74186555fc375fff9a08a02">8000e00</a>)</li> <li>Add new images, colour cards by image (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/b4c8aa7641790f5f83e6d664243a01758c53c0f7">b4c8aa7</a>)</li> <li>Add pill note on daily challenge theme (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/412077d93560dd0344d03c749599111374bdaee8">412077d</a>)</li> <li>Add pop up (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/c893218f2862c36153de4e85b5521e5deb9d00b0">c893218</a>)</li> <li>Add preview to internal tool (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/d5c789addd22c3db48daa7dbd9e35966b626d784">d5c789a</a>)</li> <li>Add remaining images (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/96584d8d86e48c939b6b88c49b9136f358023482">96584d8</a>)</li> <li>Add share button to home screen (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/ae4e0fe8233fbce9e60ccce358e0daa917b8040a">ae4e0fe</a>)</li> <li>Add Streak indicator and animations (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/d02077a1fe9e7529f4b918190c6a0a0b5fb24bfc">d02077a</a>)</li> <li>Add Streak indicator and animations (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/9042fd9a0e928d589d72766654c39d411bb92de4">9042fd9</a>)</li> <li>Add terms and privacy policy for App submission (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/eb40e75e486ad2168711672be44ac9b994867308">eb40e75</a>)</li> <li>Add When mobile first game (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/a9dc26889207cb07c059744ad7a1cf0601e0af69">a9dc268</a>)</li> <li>Added more generated images (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/e2922a7d973c0212da31c4cc041eb341db2bf7a8">e2922a7</a>)</li> <li>Added new inventions category, updated events editor (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/53acee14beaafc45619fc84658050b0018e2e4fb">53acee1</a>)</li> <li>Adding more generated images (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/e9253e23eee83193d03a7ece5f2c4bfff861ed89">e9253e2</a>)</li> <li>Adding new events (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/8916daf7fcd4e2ba4b53b35551aedfe8b660aaad">8916daf</a>)</li> <li>Adjusting events (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/9f325cdecd55c232e292497b5dbc4518552bd6ff">9f325cd</a>)</li> <li>Auto start daily challenge (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/f9e3a5a35c1cbac061ab3d8b37496bc3439bdd9f">f9e3a5a</a>)</li> <li>Better info panel (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/0b19c94d348438daf5be08dd5559b1cca996a44b">0b19c94</a>)</li> <li>Burger menu (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/5ab03c8112935fcf59c0f6a1adc70b3d30b712ae">5ab03c8</a>)</li> <li>Center first timeline card and add elastic scrolling (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/25d6aa22cc078d8002fc8a1f141384bfe431e5e3">25d6aa2</a>)</li> <li>Check for updates (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/616902557330643f5ddf91dedff62e90a7d081ff">6169025</a>)</li> <li>Clean up menu screen (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/070a40582461d1380c5ae59c42b0c6288f552983">070a405</a>)</li> <li>Clean up settings modal (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/eaa4d976e2f9bcdbd0bb36d363fa4d8dfe517fa5">eaa4d97</a>)</li> <li>Correct colours of icons / titles (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/affe5447ee4143e922845fdd469874ca03da76ea">affe544</a>)</li> <li>Create internal tool for maintaining events (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/5c6b09005cd3417dd57504a487c364b1214929e8">5c6b090</a>)</li> <li>Cycle through hand (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/20f7320fd4ba550a0dfba3fd3dde1353a1f21a6b">20f7320</a>)</li> <li>Daily becomes inifinite mode (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/95a76a11ce93f75be2f6a5366a096019fcac8440">95a76a1</a>)</li> <li>Do not close timeline at end, add restart button (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/699246a055252dcba72dca8840ea5bbf16abf9ea">699246a</a>)</li> <li>Double tap custom pills, remove challenge codes (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/f64bd7e3d24aff0b95117e431180f7499b0f8f86">f64bd7e</a>)</li> <li>Engagement (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/b541c9ed2663a4e90a312e72fa96efafdc517de9">b541c9e</a>)</li> <li>FInding new events (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/26d5decdf2ff005330d3d74c01eb808997c1ba5b">26d5dec</a>)</li> <li>Fixing info panel (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/cd64a2add48757296a5b0fef8ce7997af663243f">cd64a2a</a>)</li> <li>Game transistion animations (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/6f105f0705853aff0eb508d644636bef49b9ab5b">6f105f0</a>)</li> <li>Improve custom mode UX (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/7992c3f8eb97baf1728fd93174f4251020462555">7992c3f</a>)</li> <li>Improve timeline UI (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/8a2fa525fb06a6818a03f54bd3d2dfd13c3d4ec3">8a2fa52</a>)</li> <li>Loading screen (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/444587e04b34915b8ebfb1ce8820978b9fb30ab1">444587e</a>)</li> <li>Make app installable (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/99eb6c6f514456f563a3f4aa4417e463946307ce">99eb6c6</a>)</li> <li>Make daily challenge category based only not era based (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/833f46fecd5c13edac223a6b46fdf4dfbc1598ae">833f46f</a>)</li> <li>Make Daily game playable once per day (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/817187225dc19af4fa87ff7fb1ef73f21eff9e44">8171872</a>)</li> <li>Make install button and top bar (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/96c11cfadcce06f85477ca694b4644a0489f58e5">96c11cf</a>)</li> <li>Make settings shareable (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/a39430d6259898ac9c0365c0be30b6bf8bac4d04">a39430d</a>)</li> <li>Make the custom game work flow simpler (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/890d0411c02621523b451533f84c48559d45f479">890d041</a>)</li> <li>Mobile first design (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/f2213ed824eafe6189d40485327ea1ce4960fe4c">f2213ed</a>)</li> <li>Modern styling (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/57268ffdb753aa119249a0e689d9bab2ef6c3a1a">57268ff</a>)</li> <li>More events (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/7481be8636f7811e475d172446ae599a4a61c47a">7481be8</a>)</li> <li>More images (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/ceb876d78f61786cbfdccd61947d3efc5169a4d4">ceb876d</a>)</li> <li>More inventions (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/3a0dbb4d6d38f68c7d9ab3221484e7f1f59fdf0e">3a0dbb4</a>)</li> <li>Move version indicator (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/df5d0cbd498e7cf052dea23aded32e992ed9ab43">df5d0cb</a>)</li> <li>Multiplayer readded, back to remove cards from hand game play (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/481c4e1f28324db35bf5e696ada6944643a5b5fa">481c4e1</a>)</li> <li>Only Easy and Medium events included in daily challenge by default (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/60622f21ba96df7b8191117e7c2054634110e858">60622f2</a>)</li> <li>options persistance and ux (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/6369cdcdde47319d9b195058ca9661c1b601a97a">6369cdc</a>)</li> <li>Placement animation (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/2d92e89ef710934287e2098265dc5f19a0bde114">2d92e89</a>)</li> <li>Redesign home UI (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/4d92cfdd3952c81ad41cece78b91733e1027b981">4d92cfd</a>)</li> <li>Remove emoji (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/ee557f283309666c8a2aaea2bd9d5389d4ee7785">ee557f2</a>)</li> <li>Resize image boxes to display full image (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/9c6ecf969a8754234d38e18fb27135bff1e106b7">9c6ecf9</a>)</li> <li>SEO chores (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/6045ee9e18e5a1e56090c1058f95f8a10d01b6a6">6045ee9</a>)</li> <li>Set defualt hand size to 5 (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/00d30e5b952bc61ade1ad9c7cf07e2f7d226ce49">00d30e5</a>)</li> <li>Share shows global rank (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/23d077cb74f9acb85294a24c377655e8b2383404">23d077c</a>)</li> <li>Show leaderboard right away (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/4ee65d378c3cb7e525b48239d36f0ab001fe8717">4ee65d3</a>)</li> <li>Simplify game menus (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/6ea49bed6bd01ca7706c84035b00031a854c0415">6ea49be</a>)</li> <li>Simplify game modes (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/73aacf4ba3619fb9e05408d189e4325a29c27ded">73aacf4</a>)</li> <li>SImplify logo (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/4dec65d4a29913792148ec6ba136633e23c9e8f4">4dec65d</a>)</li> <li>uncurated-events (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/02d83b0bdf48d4d1d116031cbc55e9fc2725159a">02d83b0</a>)</li> <li>Unify text and shadows (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/3682e3c67773146a6a49d37133f6516ffe858bb4">3682e3c</a>)</li> <li>Update colour palette (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/2eb7f367fc500750280375ec5c4e147b7d744b8c">2eb7f36</a>)</li> <li>Update colour pallete (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/bc625cd17861fd9bc57ba3240b8c7e30aaf4a86e">bc625cd</a>)</li> <li>Update event difficulties. Exclude very hard events by default (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/50172be35d6733a455b3ca01d348276c871b7c3d">50172be</a>)</li> <li>Update game select UI, fix timeline snap back (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/50afd1caf4c5096ea7b5bc883a5c2b0361c2912c">50afd1c</a>)</li> <li>Update icons (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/792934e79ac19b80e9300fbd3a4d59e703455ed3">792934e</a>)</li> <li>Update install instructions (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/90ec7cb3222fa9ad3c7347eb8c1dd8bd5c11c18e">90ec7cb</a>)</li> <li>Update more images, adjust difficulty (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/7d0d050931ded0e2c4ef24f8c65e1713b8d73640">7d0d050</a>)</li> <li>Updating event images (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/c7ce664d65b1ebad3063b5335e274c760135d010">c7ce664</a>)</li> <li>Updating event images (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/6b189df6d3caf25691ade671aac820dc87517ece">6b189df</a>)</li> <li>Use react router, make challenge share directly to game (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/9d767b17fff34a64bca6d007358e368bbaadb226">9d767b1</a>)</li> <li>Use splayed cards for hand count symbol (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/ccc2535ac544597d27d25a8a739bd6a53173960b">ccc2535</a>)</li> <li>UX polish (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/b68785a0da0f13554c8ac0a92512f34579de9eca">b68785a</a>)</li> <li>Wide layout (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/36e2c7e11cff31a755311d15abffb2d1a1383e9c">36e2c7e</a>)</li> <li>Yet more new images (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/1de0e147f5dee5eeeac9f496383bdbce80602994">1de0e14</a>)</li></ul><br/><br/><h3>Bug Fixes</h3><br/><br/><ul><li>Add missing images (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/6727ad7a547ddf2b039cdf7c75c2dd62b30cda77">6727ad7</a>)</li> <li>Add more images (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/16a2ee9613e43955ff36f8f8983912f09a3ce5a8">16a2ee9</a>)</li> <li>Add wrong banner in single player (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/118b948036d7bc44dce457f56e34c14b95ba7786">118b948</a>)</li> <li>Better installation instructions (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/4d0f6bb7f4c36ab251b942dda1cf6d7cc17b36d7">4d0f6bb</a>)</li> <li>Change menu colours (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/9f55d23c087c9d8a8dab9e6a3073acc232fcfdab">9f55d23</a>)</li> <li>Correct ESlint error (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/e6cdb4dfe0bdc4e2df52f58c88f52c4dd4316ee1">e6cdb4d</a>)</li> <li>Correct number of events shared (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/9cd7c7846df769856fe04b5ac959918e6eb249b1">9cd7c78</a>)</li> <li>Correctly place wrong text in pop up, force update on new version (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/8add15075b3fbc24607e1984830a9e177fec0a00">8add150</a>)</li> <li>Fix build (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/21b21714a016edb659dac199bc0453a01867ec7d">21b2171</a>)</li> <li>Fix drag position, borders, tap for info (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/c4f98c15f47ac183b5d31c084eda2fb805b0d86c">c4f98c1</a>)</li> <li>Fix end of game in single player (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/852b3f2114302e423283c147fba837609e685e39">852b3f2</a>)</li> <li>Fix ESlint errors (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/6098424afb84628e2e60d091d60d7d19c2968733">6098424</a>)</li> <li>Fix ESlint errors (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/9fe854a017fca23263dae96e65bbad55c5bf079c">9fe854a</a>)</li> <li>Fix eslint security warning for use of roll... (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/2b1ecb3e17db9634e5f2084728770aa8a9931018">2b1ecb3</a>)</li> <li>FIx game end logic and card in hand bug (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/7e5274bc4d5240e1a57c3901ab77849e065c7e12">7e5274b</a>)</li> <li>Fix game rule text (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/1aa32b6a0efaa0e87526c89798c1cbae120f5058">1aa32b6</a>)</li> <li>Fix generation (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/dfb6342e7e47d69a8b13d498545c30cc2decb754">dfb6342</a>)</li> <li>Fix ghost card issues, drag card position, remove banner (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/025808cda75c12f71f48bb4edb9d01ae17c2dfdc">025808c</a>)</li> <li>Fix leaderboard message (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/46039e7c6c1d9541a97c9e161af0bee27eda9690">46039e7</a>)</li> <li>FIx leaderboard pop out infinite get glitch (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/fb8f3ff1724443424635402cb0358d5d19662b53">fb8f3ff</a>)</li> <li>FIx linting error (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/6ec66b0018743eb7750f19bcb5c8b844c5545c83">6ec66b0</a>)</li> <li>Fix placeholder spacing (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/93c74180d412fb7176bb61d3fc3cf1d6036335c7">93c7418</a>)</li> <li>Fix refresh timing (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/07e2b0536df6e6e8b9e5ed455d8a8b561fe7d47e">07e2b05</a>)</li> <li>fix release script (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/a7a01bde0be68f59c3488571ebecd778153c7bad">a7a01bd</a>)</li> <li>fix release script (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/b25aa77d3247f2cff60ae69786c8d9f59250d163">b25aa77</a>)</li> <li>fix release script (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/6cc7aec0174e3c98eee8819aca94375bcdd451b9">6cc7aec</a>)</li> <li>Fix sudden death logic (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/4440444021eff238d71f0789867a16baa2fa3b85">4440444</a>)</li> <li>Fix verbose names, fix detailed image load time (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/644a6acea8a8c82206630706da9bea79a87dfe85">644a6ac</a>)</li> <li>Fix zoom issue and title cutoff (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/841b3c6c044d523fc264fccce05a629522334bfb">841b3c6</a>)</li> <li>Ignore long word list file (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/7167029030092f4c6ca1be28bf8443219dadc4e6">7167029</a>)</li> <li>Improve settings UX (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/b61b1084064b94b2faa44dec6b52c59a10344f0a">b61b108</a>)</li> <li>Lower resolution of thumbnail images for faster loading (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/4bc9a24d667a3d27aed88cd84e12e041027523f7">4bc9a24</a>)</li> <li>Make challenge code readable (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/70d0e9be99cd76d25e43d6e0a16f97bdf7ddd8aa">70d0e9b</a>)</li> <li>Make next player turn more prominany (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/e65e1eb0fbed5cd0ee69598175c0bc8bb318c12a">e65e1eb</a>)</li> <li>Make settings button more visible (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/b28cac81a87cd40cadfcd92a994594d7d9724917">b28cac8</a>)</li> <li>Make timeline tick marks wider (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/a3a98599baeb4be9cf1fce490ccc0ab8c7d9e69c">a3a9859</a>)</li> <li>Make update a pop up instead of small button (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/6af2d07db549c60d7871a529b0124a9cb82f2b6d">6af2d07</a>)</li> <li>Move images folders out of main project to fix vercel dev (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/eeb6c640818715a77962395e5bef788da0129453">eeb6c64</a>)</li> <li>Only 6 categories not 7 (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/64bffd4bf244a2b0db5c8cf38c3935c45ae18ac6">64bffd4</a>)</li> <li>Prevent the view timeline page from loading all deatiled images at once (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/6a8cf28ef1c4ac84ce47460cc205ef16dc5a87aa">6a8cf28</a>)</li> <li>Prune evenys (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/640142e181a7a2cfb99ff64b23df25fb569144d2">640142e</a>)</li> <li>reduce daily challenge cards (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/065487325e9dfa07340cd826110894b5b4398996">0654873</a>)</li> <li>Refresh the leaderboard more often (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/d10d6a730a5c21ec567a64170412d0cdadab6e84">d10d6a7</a>)</li> <li>Remove duplicate events (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/a6b7e39f6a7844c02e0d14d17cd5fc4f63e50c0a">a6b7e39</a>)</li> <li>Remove references to centuries and dates (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/d59c625723aac359edf90473e8feb729c291646f">d59c625</a>)</li> <li>remove uneeded bump files (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/77873a5b8c958cefd477acd397cf2fdf5cd6bc9f">77873a5</a>)</li> <li>remove When title from game select screen (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/3842541743ebeb9ca4214d086871c450f95b6d55">3842541</a>)</li> <li>Reveal bottom bar (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/fa6facf3bae41535aba5ada1052cf30f77090e94">fa6facf</a>)</li> <li>Show install button (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/45848010b7e65ce74052910832f7095f3393b267">4584801</a>)</li> <li>Smooth out design (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/0f6eeb3cd623b5d6991ef2b81a1a340993d57d46">0f6eeb3</a>)</li> <li>Start with 5 cards in daily challenge (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/d43799087ba3db1d02a1c23b252db096e690469a">d437990</a>)</li> <li>Stop accidental leaderboard dismissal (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/19f0dab1bc3506d33fc2219cc069c719760e6fe5">19f0dab</a>)</li> <li>Sync ios version with app version (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/6a74a1c2fcff6b550b4b5d6f1c5786a4f1ecee85">6a74a1c</a>)</li> <li>Trying to fix page level scroll (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/986947945e3e44e2368593eb93f1d3433f617a48">9869479</a>)</li> <li>Update image size (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/e0c5e138947d2690ed3f7e3e60d7e91e9b1aeeb2">e0c5e13</a>)</li> <li>Update the ripple mechanics (<a href="https://github.com/Edward-Muir/when/commit/67cd1055d6920769b3215a89db6069912c695f0e">67cd105</a>)</li></ul>]]></description>
